thread.title: Marcia Proctor

author: Marcia Proctor
title: Marcia Proctor
text:
I was working to upgrade my website and was connected to Chad P, SEO Specialist, Modification Fulfillment . He took the time to do a thorough review of the site, and made excellent suggestions for modifications. He took the time to explain what should be done, and his logic behind each suggestion. He was patient and knowledgeable. I appreciate the time he took with me. I would rate him 4 stars across the board.
Marcia Proctor
